headline: Chipotle’s Asia Expansion With SPC Group Could Be a Game Changer for Chipotle Mexican Grill (CMG)
summary: Earlier this month, Chipotle Mexican Grill announced its first move into Asia through a joint venture with South Korea-based SPC Group, with plans to open restaurants in South Korea and Singapore in 2026. This marks a significant milestone for the brand, highlighting Chipotle’s belief in the growing demand for variety and convenience among Asian consumers. We'll examine how Chipotle's entry into the Asian market with SPC Group could shape its growth prospects and investment narrative. Find...
